{"word":"G214 - ἀλαλάζω - alalázō - al-al-ad'-zo - Tinkle","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀλαλάζω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">alalázō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">al-al-ad'-zo</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Tinkle</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - அழுது, புலம்பு, ஒசையிடு"},{"paragraph":"1. to repeat frequently the cry"},{"paragraph":"2. to utter a joyful shout"},{"paragraph":"3. to wail, lament"},{"paragraph":"4. to ring loudly, to clang"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <b>&#x03B1;&#x0313;&#x03BB;&#x03B1;&#x03BB;&#x03B7;&#x0301;</b> <b>alale&#x0304;</b> (a <i>shout</i>, <i>&ldquo;halloo&rdquo;</i>); to <i>vociferate</i>, that is, (by implication) to <i>wail</i>; figuratively to <i>clang:</i> - tinkle, wail.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}